OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FA huge wildfire which destroyed a vast
OL,7,Fswathe of moorland in North Yorkshire
OL,8,Fwas caused by people cooking on an
OL,9,Fopen flame, investigators have said.
OL,11,FDescribed as the biggest blaze seen by
OL,12,Fsome firefighters in their careers,
OL,13,Fthe incident on Langdale and
OL,14,FFylingdales Moor, in the North York
OL,15,FMoors, left the landscape charred,
OL,16,Fforced the evacuation of homes and
OL,17,Fdestroyed wildlife habitats.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
