PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FInvestigators have now revealed last
OL,7,FAugust's fire was started by a naked
OL,8,Fflame, probably from a gas burner,
OL,9,Fbarbecue or campfire.
OL,11,FChief fire officer Jonathan Dyson, of
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService (NYFRS), said it was a "stark
OL,14,Freminder of how quickly wildfires can
OL,15,Ftake hold, particularly in hot, dry
OL,16,Fand windy conditions".
OL,18,F"Moorland, forestry and rural
OL,19,Fenvironments are extremely vulnerable,
OL,20,Fand even small flames can have
OL,21,Fdevastating consequences," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
