PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FA major incident was declared after
OL,7,Fthe fire broke out on 11 August, 11
OL,8,Fmiles inland from Robin Hood's Bay.
OL,10,FAt its height it covered an area of
OL,11,F25km sq and burned at temperatures of
OL,12,F600C. Firefighters from across the
OL,13,Fcountry were drafted in to help. The
OL,14,Fincident caused several blasts from
OL,15,Funexploded Second World War bombs.
OL,17,FIt took three months for the fire to
OL,18,Ffully extinguish.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
