PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FFull recovery of the landscape, which
OL,7,Fis an area of special scientific
OL,8,Finterest, could take hundreds or even
OL,9,Fthousands of years, environmental
OL,10,Fscientists said at the time.
OL,12,FOn Thursday NYFRS said the operation
OL,13,Fto control and extinguish the fire had
OL,14,Fbeen "one of the most complex multi-
OL,15,Fagency incidents the service has ever
OL,16,Fattended", made more complicated by
OL,17,Fthe remote location and low water
OL,18,Fsupplies last summer.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
