PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FInvestigators gave their conclusions
OL,7,Fafter spending months evaluating
OL,8,Fwitness statements, inspecting the
OL,9,Fsite and reviewing footage.
OL,11,FThursday's findings were used to
OL,12,Freiterate warnings about lighting
OL,13,Fbarbeques or campfires in areas of
OL,14,Fopen moorland, including to bring home
OL,15,Fany litter and not to dispose of lit
OL,16,Fcigarettes.
OL,18,FMr Dyson added: "In response to this
OL,19,Fincident, we are reviewing and
OL,20,Fstrengthening our wildfire provision.
OL,26,@zD@QOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
