OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,F"This includes increasing the number
OL,7,Fof specialist wildfire teams,
OL,8,Fenhancing our equipment, vehicles and
OL,9,Fprotective clothing, and putting
OL,10,Fformal agreements in place with
OL,11,Fpartner organisations to support us
OL,12,Fduring major incidents. We are also
OL,13,Fprogressing work to improve our
OL,14,Fability to deliver large volumes of
OL,15,Fwater at wildfire incidents."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@]O]
