FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FJo Coles, the deputy mayor for
OL,7,Fpolicing, fire and crime in North
OL,8,FYorkshire, said the firefight was "an
OL,9,Fextraordinary combined effort,
OL,10,Ftackling one of the largest wild fires
OL,11,Fever in the United Kingdom".
OL,13,FShe added: "As a result of the
OL,14,Fchanging climate, our beautiful
OL,15,Fmoorlands are unfortunately
OL,16,Fincreasingly vulnerable to wildfires
OL,17,Fand it's vital we all do everything we
OL,18,Fcan to learn lessons and focus on how
OL,19,Fto prevent future incidents like this."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
