PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772118239
OL,3,CInvestigation finds huge moorland fire
OL,4,Cstarted by open-air cooking
OL,6,FLarge-scale moorland wildfires have
OL,7,Fbeen an increasingly common occurrence
OL,8,Fin recent years due to warmer weather
OL,9,Fand drier summers, with many having
OL,10,Fstarted by barbecues and campfires.
OL,12,FIn 2024, a huge fire on Meltham Moor
OL,13,Fin West Yorkshire which burned for
OL,14,Fthree days was later attributed to a
OL,15,Fdisposable barbecue.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
